title: Factor This finance and development roundup: AES, Alliant, CleanChoice, CMBlu, Encore
description: AES Indiana brings solar+storage online, Alliant fires up two new BESS, CleanChoice triples its generation capacity, CMBlu inks a deal with Uniper, and Encore starts construction in Illinois.
